review_title: Good sound, and decently comfortable headphones
reviews:
Good sound, and decently comfortable headphones.
After 8 months of usage the battery discharge faster (after 1-2 hour usage a day batteries are low) and when the battery is low, the sound gets cut often.
A minor issue is that the buttons on the headphones makes a faint click sound when running with the headphones (because the buttons moves a little bit).
They lasted me 1 year after breaking.
